{"id": "1424747562463793192", "channel_id": "1421787273732554854", "type": 19, "author_id": "302718766289256448", "author_name": "zekiei", "author_bot": false, "content": "After comparing multiple accounts, it seems to be as follow:\n* You get 1 \"compensation\" for every time you got 2 standard in a row in all previous timeless (can see how many you have in banner rules).\n* Each compensation means the next SSR will be the target wod or awaker\n* The 2/1 rule between target wod and awaker only counts the last and current timeless, not the one before that", "timestamp": "2025-10-06T13:18:09.421000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["277927692735873035"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1424634751746310185", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1421787273732554854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3.3.0 停服维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
